NUMBER 201
NAME Main Street, Gatehouse
MONSTER_GROUP 1
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Here is where the hustle and bustle of the city moves towards the wilderness
outside. West of here lies the bazaar where a lot of the cities commerce
takes place, the street between here and there is almost always chaotic.
Looming to the east is the newly built inner gate of the massive gatehouse.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 6908
EXIT ABOVE 2152
ITEM 0 1327 ADJ1=189 ADJ2=1620 VAL1=6900 VAL2=6900 VAL3=6900 UNLOCKED OPEN
ITEM 1 943 ADJ1=169 ADJ2=1414 ADJ3=577 VAL1=6900 VAL2=6901 VAL3=6900 OPEN UNLOCKED
EXTEND 1 to the north gate tower
IFENTRY
  IFVAR INTNUM6 = 2
    GMMSG Honk! %N is a newbie.
    ECHO PLAYER [Type HELP to access the help system. Type ASSIST to request a gamemaster as soon as one is available. Type ADVICE for hints on getting started.]
		PLREVENT 4
		CONTPLREVENT
