NUMBER 204
NAME Bazaar Northeast
MONSTER_GROUP 1
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
This section of the bazaar is remarkably free of the stalls and shouting
merchants that are prevalent elsewhere. Perhaps it has something to do with
the imposing building that stands on the corner. Made of stone, and free of
any color, its only decoration is the words, "ETERNITY, INC." written above
the single door leading in. The building could probably win the award for
drabbest building in Fayd. When your business is death insurance, it might be
considered poor taste to have garish decorations adorn your building. A door
provides an entrance.
*DESCRIPTION_END
