*DESCRIPTION_START
Piles of wood and brick evidence on going construction. At one time this
corner of the bazaar held only stay animals and empty stalls. Now an ongoing
urban renewal project is constructing new buildings and patching the street.
A bronze plaque is mounted over a newly painted arch that leads into a
courtyard.
*DESCRIPTION_END
