*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
The saloon is a sprawling, two-story place. The entrance is a doorway with a
pair of swinging doors set into it. From inside you can hear the sounds of
people having a good time and drinking a little too much. There are no windows
on the first floor, you notice, though a few look down at you from the second.
*DESCRIPTION_END
