NUMBER 206
NAME Bazaar Center
MONSTER_GROUP 1
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The center of the bazaar bustles with activity. From the sizzle of roast
mutton on spits, to the cries of hawkers there is almost too much for the
senses to absorb. Apart from the interruption of merchants offering you their
wares, one might spend an enjoyable afternoon here. Many street performers,
from jugglers to minstrels, amuse the crowds gathered near a large marble
fountain.
*DESCRIPTION_END
