NUMBER 223
NAME Bazaar Northwest
MONSTER_GROUP 1
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Grand Avenue winds into the bazaar from the north of here. Dominating the
western side is the large dome-shaped structure owned by CyberTech Ltd.
Within, practitioners of the most ancient arts labor to rediscover the wonders
known to Man before the Cataclysm. Those who can afford their prices are able
to obtain technological implants that can improve or even replace natural
parts of the anatomy. A glass door allows entry into the building.
*DESCRIPTION_END
