NUMBER 240
NAME Broadway & Church
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
MONSTER_GROUP 1
*DESCRIPTION_START
Broadway is intersected by beginning of Church Street which continues north.
One easily recognizes the wide variety of religious ornamentation worn by
travellers going that way. It is the location of the majority of Fayd's
temples. You can hear vociferous theological debates even from here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
