NUMBER 241
NAME Church Street
OUTDOOR_OTHER
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The temple of Rorin stands proudly, its gleaming buttresses and burnished
doors resplendent the late sun. The intricate stained glass windows look
over the street like multihued eyes. Two guards dressed in gold and red
stand on either side of the doors, proof against any impropriety toward
Rorin or his followers.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 7047
EXIT N 6945
EXIT ABOVE 2152
ITEM 0 350 VAL2=1190
ITEM 1 249
ITEM 2 72
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The window is formed of concentric bands of stained glass, done in the warm
tones of gold, yellow, orange, and crimson. Seven tongues of flame, made of
pure silver encircle the orb.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB GO 2
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  IFVAR DISGUISED = 1
    ECHO PLAYER You are repelled from the opening as a voice booms in your mind, "You may not be hidden when standing before Justice."
