This intersection is dedication to one of the most honorable wolflings
known to the citizens of Fayd in the reign of Frederick Kentaurus III.
Kai Wolgrad was instrumental in the defense of the city a number of times
as well as being a noble in the truest sense of the word.
*DESCRIPTION_END
