CHANNEL 500
ECHOCHAN 500
DROPLOC 371
*DESCRIPTION_START
This oval, sand covered space is the arena proper. Walls rise up from the sand
to protect the fans from the combatants. Small ducts in the walls will flood
the arena with water in case an Aqua-Combat is being fought. Though fresh sand
is sprinkled over the arena floor between combats, there are still patches of
bloody evidence that arena combat is more than just fun and games. A tunnel
leads down to the beast pits, and an opening to the southwest leads back to
the locker rooms.
*DESCRIPTION_END
