MONSTER_GROUP 1
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
The courtyard is edged with the the wide pane windows of new shops, but only
two are occupied. The window near the red door reads, "Loopo the Butcher." The
window near the blue door is emblazoned with the promising words: "Aunt Emma's
Bakery Treats." In the center of the courtyard a large barrel has been halved
and used as a planter box. It is currently full of bright red flowers. The
courtyard continues south.
*DESCRIPTION_END
