These are the stuffy business offices of Eternity Inc. Here you may buy
insurance that will allow for reconstruction of the body should accidental
death occur. A bored looking agent is leaning on a desk heaping with stacks
of papers. A doorway leads back to the bazaar, and a stone stair leads down
to a storage basement.
