Number 6921
Name Windrunner Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Standing out from the other parts of the street is a wrought iron fence.
Within the fence there is a field of wildflowers where honeybees and
hummingbirds dart from blossom to blossom. A few fruit trees stand here
and there.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 6920
EXIT E 6922
