The homes here are stylishly built and most are surrounded by a variety of
fences, some covered in ivy and other creeping plants adorned with flowers
and blossoms. The genial folk of neighborhood are more than eager to share
a story or two to visitors of Fayd.
*DESCRIPTION_END
