NUMBER 6939
NAME Main Street
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The shops and buildings taper off here. Down the street a little way
you can just make out the palace gate and the towers and parapets that
are part of the palace itself. The street here is less populated by
people and more populated by trees and flowers. Carriages carrying those
coming from and going to the palace roll down the street in an orderly
fashion. Several lawkeeps watch those who pass by, ever vigilant in
doing their part to protect the royal family.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 251
EXIT W 250
