Here at the three-way intersection, the traffic is a little thicker and more
congested. To the north is Scimitar Street, and Broadway continues on its
east-west track. Most of the traffic continues on Broadway, and a few
pedestrians and wagons peel off the east-west flow to turn north.
*DESCRIPTION_END
