NAME Grand Avenue
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Brightly-colored awning hangs over the front of each of the shops set up
in a precise row. Delightful smells and sounds escape every time a door
is opened. Young matrons, with large baskets on their arms, and tiny
children tagging on their apron strings, weave and dodge past each other
to get to the door they wish to enter.
*DESCRIPTION_END
