OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The traffic thickens here closer to the Bazaar. Merchants heading for
their businesses, and priests followed closely by alcolytes mingle in
with lawkeepers and the common people, each hurrying to complete their
own tasks. The bustle and activity here doesn't encourage loitering.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 362
