NUMBER 6981
NAME Pleasant Street
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The financial district gives way completely to residences on this part
of the street. Lined on either side by small, quaint homes, the street
takes on a cozy feel. Tiny gardens play host to singing birds and
colorful butterflies, attracted by the fragrant blossoms that grow here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
