DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
The very end of Park Avenue, this circular courtyard is surrounded by
imposing stone walls with a gate at the south end. The gate is flanked
by two pairs of extremely vigilant royal guards. Through the gate, the
gardens of the palace can be seen.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 274
ITEM 0 68 ADJ1=169 VAL1=100 VAL2=375 LOCKED
IFSAY open_the_gates!
 IFVAR INTNUM3 = 44
