Number 7011
Name Main Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand before the grand splendor of the new Palace Gates. The walls
supporting them are taller than they were as well, and flanking towers
stand higher than the walls. The length of Main Street extends east
all the way to the gate.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 7012
ITEM 0 68 VAL2=1908 ADJ1=189 ADJ2=1181 CLOSED LOCKED
;
Number 7012
Name Main Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Just outside the gate of the Palace, most of the traffic here are people
of the court. Pages, courtiers and nobles alike are scurrying around,
each on their own agenda. On the south side of the street is a newly
finished building. The building is a magnificent stone edifice of stately
grace. Banners from the building flaunt royal blue fields with a tiger's
paw on them. Two pairs of Royal Guards flank the stone arch that leads to
the interior. Another two pair stand at the base of the stone steps that
rise to the arch.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 7013
EXIT W 7011
ITEM 0 60 VAL2=7012
;
Number 7013
Name Main Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Beautiful new three story residences here are the rave of the city. There
are three of them along the street, two on the north, one of the south.
Various scribes and runners are lurking around the entrances to all three
of the buildings, as if they know the inhabitants might need them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 7014
EXIT W 7012
ITEM 6 692 VAL2=7515
;
Number 7014
Name Main Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
A two story building on the south side of the street seems to have quite a
few Crimson Band and Royal Guard soldiers hanging outside as well as coming
and going. Just to the east, twin guard towers rise above the buildings
with a bridge crossing over the newly laid cobbles.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 7013
ITEM 0 68 ADJ1=97 VAL2=7015 OPEN UNLOCKED
ITEM 1 405
ITEM 2 405
IFSAY Seal_the_gate!
  IFITEM 0 CLOSED
    IFITEM 0 UNLOCKED
      IFVAR ORG = 6
        LOCK 0
        AFFECT 6900
        LOCK 0
        AFFECT 201
        ECHO ALL A squad from the Royal Guard comes out with a pair of massive beams and barricades the inner gate.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ORG = 3
        LOCK 0
        AFFECT 6900
        LOCK 0
        AFFECT 201
        ECHO ALL A squad from the Royal Guard comes out with a pair of massive beams and barricades the inner gate.
      ENDIF
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER The gate is already locked.
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The gate is not closed yet.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Open_the_gate!
  IFITEM 0 CLOSED
    IFITEM 0 LOCKED
      IFVAR ORG = 6
        UNLOCK 0
        OPEN 0
        AFFECT 6900
        UNLOCK 0
        OPEN 0
        AFFECT 201
      ECHO ALL A squad from the Royal Guard comes out and removes the two massive beams which barricades the inner gate.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ORG = 3
        UNLOCK 0
        OPEN 0
        AFFECT 6900
        UNLOCK 0
        OPEN 0
        AFFECT 201
        ECHO ALL A squad from the Royal Guard comes out and removes the two massive beams which barricades the inner gate.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The gate is already open.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
