Name Main Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Just to the west, north and south of the road, twin towers guard the road
to the palace. A huge double gate awaits to swing shut to protect the Royal
Family should the need arise. You see at least a dozen alert soldiers from
both the Royal Guard and the Crimson Band. Overhead, you notice that there
is a bridge between the towers some fifteen feet over the street.
*DESCRIPTION_END
