NUMBER 7016
NAME Main Street
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The streets and buildings are a lot more immaculate this close to the
palace. Several guard columns pass by, keeping time and walking in
tight formation. To the west you can see the palace gate and the towers
that guard it, and looking up at the palace you can see people moving
about behind most of the windows.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 7017
EXIT W 7015
IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can hear the rhythmic marching of palace guards to the west.
ENDIF
;
Number 7017
Name Main Street
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
This newly built road leads between Kai's Corner and the palace. The
cobbles are freshly laid and tightly packed. Several buildings are in
construction here, but you can see the newly finished Royal Barracks
on the north side of the street slightly east of here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 250
EXIT W 7016
;
Number 7018
Name Kentaurus Boulevard
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Narrow brick townhomes stand shoulder-to-shoulder, their tightly peaked
roofs reaching skyward. Though closely constructed, each home appears to
have been built using the best materials and craftmanship. Individuality
shines through in the painted facades and ornate scrollwork. Lacking space
for yards and gardens, the inhabitants have created lush landscapes on
patios and verandas using potted trees and beautifully formed trellises
covered in bright flowers. Kentaurus Blvd continues to the north and south,
Darkwood Road lies to the west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 7019
EXIT S 2677
EXIT W 7039
; potted trees
ITEM 0 881 ADJ1=1222
;
Number 7019
Name Kentaurus Boulevard
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Beautifully painted and richly appointed townhomes line each side of the
boulevard. Glancing at the homes, you see that hours of work have gone into
even the smallest details. The scrollwork along the eaves has been carved
into the shapes of fairies mermaids and the long wooden bannisters, framing
in the patios, have been lovingly sanded and stained to a rich golden glow.
Potted flowers and shrubs create pockets of natural beauty on the patios and
verandas. Kentaurus Avenue continues to the south and to the north, Deepwood
Avenue begins.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 7020
EXIT S 7018
;
Number 7020
Name Deepwood Avenue
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Deepwood Avenue stretches out before you to the west framed by rows of pine
trees and two ancient, ivy covered walls, obscuring much of the view of the
huge estates. Judging by the size of the rooftops that are visible to you,
it is fair to say that this is a well-to-do neighborhood. From the south
you can hear the hustle and bustle of Kentaurus Avenue.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 7019
EXIT W 7021
ITEM 0 420 ADJ1=784 ADJ2=407
ITEM 1 229 ADJ1=234
;
Number 7021
Name Deepwood Avenue
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Deepwood Avenue continues to the east and west. Squirrels race about the pine trees and scurry atop the walls, assaulting you with their chatter from all sides. The many trees here obscure much of the sky, their branches weaving together above your h
ead.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 7020
EXIT W 7022
ITEM 0 420 ADJ1=784 ADJ2=407
ITEM 1 229 ADJ1=234
;
Number 7022
Name Deepwood Avenue
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
The sound of frantic barking greets you as you continue along Deepwood Avenue and you assume that one of the opulant estates must contain a kennel. The unrelenting barking urges you to press on to the east or west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
