*DESCRIPTION_START
Servants of the various houses tend to congregate at this section of Deepwood Avenue. You overhear snatches of gossip from the servants enjoying a short break before returning to their duties at the estates that are prominent in this neighborhood. As
 you make your way along the street, the conversation abruptly ends and unfriendly stares imply that they wish you to be on your way.
*DESCRIPTION_END
