*DESCRIPTION_START
An especially large house towers above the old wall to the north. Through the branches of the pine trees, you glimpse hints of marble and glass. Squirrels leap from branch to branch in the trees before your eyes as you try to get a better look at the
 beautiful house. Giving up hope of a better view, you see that Deepwood Avenue continues to the east and west.
*DESCRIPTION_END
