Name Deepwood Avenue
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Trees line the street like pillars and the high walls on either side of Deepwood Avenue almost make you feel as if you were in the wooded hall of a great forest king. Only the rooftops glimpsed behind the walls break this illusion. As you continue al
ong your way, your mind seems to wander back to tales of aelfen kings.
*DESCRIPTION_END
