Number 7026
Name Deepwood Avenue
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
The delightful songs of the birds overhead put a bounce in your step as you continue along the Avenue. Watching the birds as you pass by, you notice that the feathered bards stop singing long enough to snatch the berries growing on the vine-covered
walls. Glimpses of reflections in the windows are all you can see of the mansions hidden behind the trees and gates.
*DESCRIPTION_END
