NUMBER 7032
NAME Manor Row
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The homes on the part of Manor Row are modest and tasteful, displaying
elegant gardens and well manicured grounds. The trees here are tall and cast
great swathes of shade across the cobble-stoned avenue. One gracious home-
owner has placed a wooden bench in the shade of a drooping willow, creating
an inviting place to relax on warm summer days.
*DESCRIPTION_END
