Name Darkwood Road
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
The magnificent gardens, for which Darkwood Avenue is famous, surround the beautiful homes with a riot of colors. The air here is fragrant with the scent of flowers and trees. Taking in a deep breath, as you make your way down the cobblestoned avenue
, you feel refreshed. To the west the avenue intersects with Manor Road and to the east Darkwood Avenue continues.
*DESCRIPTION_END
