The bushes surrounding many of the homes here have been trimmed to resemble animals. Green bears dance for the pleasure of leafy griffons in the beautiful gardens around you. Many of the homes along the avenue favor stained glass windows and oaken do
ors carved with beautiful images. You almost feel transported to some fantastical world as you continue along Darkwood Avenue.
