You travel across a beautifully carved stone bridge. It gracefully arches over a small man-made pond in which a few swans swim in lazy circles. The path down to the pond and surrounding homes is blocked by a gate. From the middle of the bridge you ca
n see some of the beautiful homes and gardens which border the pond. To the east and west the bridge ends and Darkwood Avenue continues.
