The elegant gardens and homes of Darkwood Avenue stretch out before you. Each garden is a masterpiece in it's own right but together they combine to create one of the most beautiful streets in Fayd. To the west can be seen a small bridge and the gard
ens and homes which make up Darkwood Avenue. To the east the avenue intersects Kentaurus Avenue.
