ITEM 0 420
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The brick wall is tall and sturdy. As your eyes scan the length of the wall,
they are met by those of a stern guard from behind a gate. He says nothing
but the look in his eyes makes you feel that you are not welcome here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
NUMBER 7042
NAME Hardwood Avenue
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Family crests, displayed on closed gates, portray a menagerie of fanciful
beasts and brightly colored symbols. Flags and banners, displaying the
various family colors, can just barely be made out from behind the large
brick walls. To the east and the west, Hardwood Avenue continues.
*DESCRIPTION_END
