NUMBER 7045
NAME Hardwood Avenue
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
As you continue to move along Hardwood Avenue, a particulary old mansion
reminds you of the rumors you have heard of several of the large estates
being haunted in this section of the city. Some of the ancient beautiful
estates along the avenue predate even the cataclysm and if spirits prefer
to dwell in any section of town, this is probably it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
