*DESCRIPTION_START
A few shops and government buildings stand on the outskirts of the Bazaar,
near the hustle and bustle, but not directly in its path. Beggars and
panhandlers stand on the sidewalks, waiting to ply their trade on the more
wealthy-looking citizenry that pass by.
*DESCRIPTION_END
