NUMBER 7050
NAME Broadway
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_OTHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
Ancient homes, some of the oldest in the city, stand in stately splendor
on lush green lawns and protected by tall, leafy trees. One of the quaint
old homes has been converted into a museum for Faydian Art and Antiques.
Funded by patrons of the museum, this home is very well maintained and has
been recently painted and refurbished.
*DESCRIPTION_END
